💧Clean, calm, and deeply nourished, thanks to my newest skincare obsession!🤍
Trying out the 1025 Dokdo Toner by ROUND LAB via @maccaron_beauty has been such a refreshing experience. I wasn’t expecting much at first, but this toner quickly became one of those rare products I genuinely look forward to using every day.

Formulated with deep sea water from Ulleungdo, it’s incredibly rich in minerals that hydrate, soothe, and support the skin barrier perfect for tired, stressed, or sensitive skin like mine.

🤍 Texture & Feel:
The consistency is watery-light, but don’t let that fool you, it delivers hydration that lasts. It absorbs in seconds, no stickiness, no fragrance, just comfort.

💧 How My Skin Feels:
Within a few uses, my skin started feeling more balanced and less reactive. Redness reduced, and those dry areas around my cheeks? Gone. I even noticed my skin looking a bit brighter and more even-toned.

Why It’s a Winner:
• Ideal for sensitive, dehydrated skin
• Great for layering or toner-soaked pads
• Barrier-loving ingredients with no irritation
• Fragrance-free and gentle enough for daily use

It’s simple, effective, and honestly a skin savior in a bottle. If you’re building a calm, gentle routine, this deserves a spot.

☀️💛 Two skincare heroes that have been saving my oily-combo skin this summer:

Let’s talk about the sunscreen first—because this one’s truly worth the hype.
🔸 SPF 50+ PA++++ gives solid broad-spectrum protection, and the best part?
It’s completely oil-free. No stickiness, no greasy finish—just a smooth, soft feel that sits well even under makeup.
🔸 It contains 1% Ceramide Complex that actually repairs and supports your skin barrier while you’re out in the sun.
🔸 Paired with 1% Vitamin C Complex, it’s helping me fight free radicals and fade dullness gradually.
🔸 Oh—and it’s water-resistant, so perfect for sweaty days or a quick outdoor run.

Now to the Oil-Free Moisturizer 💧
It’s lightweight, non-sticky, and honestly feels like nothing on the skin—but does everything.

✨ Vitamin C Complex is slowly helping even out my skin tone.

What I love most about this combo is that it’s dermatologist-developed for Indian skin—so it doesn’t just sit on top, it actually works with what your skin needs in this weather.

📌 If you’ve been on the hunt for non-greasy, barrier-supporting, brightening care—this duo is the one to try.
